i>Alcox</i>. The family trace their descent from an Alcocke family who emigrated from England to MA with John Winthrop (see   Winthrop  ) in 1630."]}]},{"name":"John","type":"FIRST","meanings":["Greek: the Lord gave graciously; whom Jehovah gave; whom Jehovah bestowed."],"variants":[]}],"lifeSummary":"John Alcock was born in 1325, in Nottinghamshire, England, United Kingdom. He had at least 1 son with Mrs. John Alcock. He died in 1410, in Yorkshire, England, United Kingdom, at the age of 85."},"et":{"1325–1410":"1325–1410","1330–Female":"1330–Surnud","1400–1490":"1400–1490","1 January 1400":"1. jaanuar 1400","1325":"1325","1400":"1400","1410":"1410","1330":"1330","1490":"1490","Yorkshire, England":"Yorkshire, Inglismaa, United Kingdom","Beverly, Yorkshire, England":"Beverley, Yorkshire, England","Chastrefeld, Nottinghamshire, England":"Nottinghamshire, Inglismaa, United Kingdom"},"fi":{"1325–1410":"1325–1410","1330–Female":"1330–Kuollut","1400–1490":"1400–1490","1 January 1400":"1. tammikuuta 1400","1325":"1325","1400":"1400","1410":"1410","1330":"1330","1490":"1490","Yorkshire, England":"Yorkshire, Englanti, Yhdistynyt kuningaskunta","Beverly, Yorkshire, England":"Beverley, Yorkshire, England","Chastrefeld, Nottinghamshire, England":"Nottinghamshire, Englanti, Yhdistynyt kuningaskunta"},"fr":{"1325–1410":"1325–1410","1330–Female":"1330–Décédée","1400–1490":"1400–1490","1 January 1400":"1 janvier 1400","1325":"1325","1400":"1400","1410":"1410","1330":"1330","1490":"1490","Yorkshire, England":"Everwyck, Angleterre, Royaume-Uni","Beverly, Yorkshire, England":"Beverley, Everwyck, Angleterre","Chastrefeld, Nottinghamshire, England":"Nottinghamshire, Angleterre, Royaume-Uni","lifeSummary":"John Alcock est né en 1325, à Nottinghamshire, Angleterre, Royaume-Uni. Il a eu au moins 1 fils avec Mrs. John Alcock. Il est décédé en 1410, à Everwyck, Angleterre, Royaume-Uni, à l’âge de 85 ans."},"de":{"1325–1410":"1325–1410","1330–Female":"1330–Verstorben","1400–1490":"1400–1490",